last_episode_to_air.name: Marrs Family Farmhouse Renovation
last_episode_to_air.overview: It's a mix of emotions as the Marrs take on a special renovation of their own family farmhouse. Dave and Jenny face the unexpected and embrace some big changes as they prepare to say goodbye to the old home and adjust to their new space.

name: Fixer to Fabulous
overview: Dave and Jenny Marrs are a couple who renovate and sell historic houses in their hometown of Bentonville, Arkansas.

episodes.name: From Craftsman to Creole Cottage
episodes.overview: A couple who loves New Orleans-style architecture asks Dave and Jenny transform their classic Craftsman into a Creole cottage. The dynamic duo remodels each room with unique touches like antique doors, homemade gas lanterns and an airy front porch.

episodes.name: Classic Colonial Meets Modern-Day Makeover
episodes.overview: Jenny and Dave are challenged to completely overhaul a historic Dutch Colonial home for a couple of farm owners and their two small children. While keeping the home's history and character, they come up with a plan for a open-concept kitchen, a one-of-a-kind playroom and an unexpected pop of color on the exterior.

episodes.name: Outdated to Modern
episodes.overview: A family that owns a local brewery purchased an older home rich with history, but the outdated rooms and obsolete features create many challenges. Dave and Jenny Marrs hatch a plan to overhaul the space by adding creative and personal touches like a custom, handmade beer tap, brand-new master suite and stunning outdoor kitchen.

episodes.name: Century-Old Farmhouse Becomes New Forever Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny help a couple update their century-old farmhouse so that it better accommodates large family gatherings. Their main goal is to improve flow and add modern amenities without stripping the home of its unique country character. The plan calls for a complete kitchen overhaul with a custom concrete sink and a couple surprising flourishes that celebrate the family’s 100-year history in the home.

episodes.name: A Drab Victorian Gets a Fab Facelift
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny Marrs help a woman turn her historic 1905 home into a beautiful Victorian retreat. But they have their work cut out for them with its shoddy, unfinished contracting work throughout the living room, kitchen, master bedroom and back porch.

episodes.name: From Nightmare Cabin to Family Dream Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny modernize a couple’s rundown log cabin while keeping its historic integrity intact. The top-to-bottom transformation includes new amenities like a custom live-edge bar, outdoor shower and a brand-new porch.

episodes.name: A Bigger Kitchen for a Growing Family
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny Marrs overhaul an expecting couple's outdated, 1970s home into a space that feels welcoming for their growing family. They create an open, airy kitchen and a backyard that will be the envy of every kid and grown-up in the neighborhood.

episodes.name: Entertaining Oasis
episodes.overview: A married couple owns a wine bar and loves to entertain, but their home's not quite ready for guests due to its compartmentalized layout, unstable balconies and an enormous, rotting tree.

episodes.name: Surprise Renovation For First-Time Homeowner
episodes.overview: A new homeowner's first place needs work, so her parents recruit Dave and Jenny to pull off a surprise renovation while she's out of town. The Marrs race the clock to create a quaint, warm and welcoming home that matches the homeowner's tastes perfectly.

episodes.name: Dreary Home Gets Bright Update
episodes.overview: A baking aficionado and her husband want to convert their dark, oddly constructed home into a bright and welcoming space for them and their kids. Dave and Jenny must tackle its fortress facade and 1970s interior to bring the home into the 21st century. While Dave encounters odd structural issues, Jenny battles one of her biggest fears as she updates the exterior's extremely high, rusted balconies.

episodes.name: Historic Home Overhaul
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny Marrs transform the a family's historic, 1893 house. From turning an attic space into two bedrooms to completely renovating the kitchen and living area, they pull out all the stops to give the family of five their first home.

episodes.name: A New Lease on Life
episodes.overview: After overcoming serious health issues, Troy Ward, along with his wife, Melode, and daughter, Ally, purchase a house on the lake, hoping to make it their forever home, where they can start living life to the fullest.

episodes.name: She Said "Yes!"
episodes.overview: A newly engaged couple recently purchased their first property, but the outdated and closed-off interior doesn't fit their needs. Dave and Jenny expand the floor plan, overhaul the kitchen and transform the backyard to create an entertaining hot spot.

episodes.name: Family House With History
episodes.overview: A couple's 19th-century home has been in their family for five generations, and they want to update it to fit their lifestyle. Dave and Jenny renovate the space while preserving the historic charm so the home can be passed down for generations to come.

episodes.name: A Home to Love
episodes.overview: A woman made an offer on a 1902 house before her husband could see it, and he believes it's too outdated to be their forever home. Dave and Jenny work to renovate and update the spaces while preserving its original charm that she loves.

episodes.name: Rustic Cabin to Contemporary Retreat
episodes.overview: A family that survived a devastating house fire buys a home on the lake so they can enjoy their favorite spot year-round. However, the lack of space doesn't fit their needs, so they ask Dave and Jenny to completely overhaul the rustic cabin.

episodes.name: Old Dojo to Modern Mojo
episodes.overview: A couple bought a karate studio as an investment property but when life threw them a curveball, they decided to downsize. With Dave and Jenny's help, they want to transform the commercial space into a home complete with industrial and modern charm.

episodes.name: An Old Rancher Gets a Chef-Inspired Facelift
episodes.overview: Two restaurant owners live in the house her grandfather built, but it's too old-fashioned for their taste and two active boys. When they call on Dave and Jenny to update their outdated ranch, the results are inspiring, modern and ready for entertaining.

episodes.name: A Life-Changing, Marrs Family Renovation
episodes.overview: When Jenny's parents decided to make the move to Bentonville, Arkansas, from Florida, the Marrs were thrilled to have them closer ... but after months of living under the same roof, it's time for Joan and Steve to have a fabulous dream home of their own.

episodes.name: A Boring House Turns Into a Boho-Chic Rental
episodes.overview: Tired of their tight quarters in New Jersey, two best friends were happy to be transferred back to Bentonville, Arkansas, for work. Luckily, Dave and Jenny Marrs have a rental property that is ready to be custom-renovated with cool Caribbean style.

episodes.name: Dysfunctional Rancher Becomes a Family-Friendly Home
A Closed-Off House Turns Character-Filled Home
Historic House Gets Pretty Pink Overhaul
Lakeside Retreat Gets Kid-Friendly Upgrade
episodes.overview: A couple bought a waterfront home with a stunning, panoramic view of the lake for their whole family to enjoy. Dave and Jenny have their work cut out for them as they turn this humdrum house into an artsy, kid-friendly home with its own indoor treehouse!

episodes.name: Modern Lodge Chalet at Long Last
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny complete a home with a kitchen that has lots of storage and a cozy screened porch.

episodes.name: From Boring 90s House to Stylish Family Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny incorporate bourbon and baseball into their home design.

episodes.name: Lakehouse Dreams Do Come True
episodes.overview: A couple bought a house on Lake Windsor, but the spacious property needs lots of work.

episodes.name: Holiday Surprise
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny gift the Bella Vista Animal Shelter with a very merry renovation.

episodes.name: Rough Rancher Made Modern Farmhouse
episodes.overview: A businesswoman has had several houses built by Dave and Jenny in the past, but this time she is looking to settle down in her forever home.

episodes.name: Boring Rancher to Beautiful Bungalow
episodes.overview: A couple hosts a lot of international students in their home, and they need Dave and Jenny's help with transforming their small rancher into a welcoming, worldly and eclectic place where visitors and family members can gather.

episodes.name: New Tudor Home in Time for a Newborn
Funky, Modern Home With a Pool
episodes.overview: A father wants to turn his half-finished bachelor pad into a modern home for entertaining that reflects his style. Dave and Jenny update the house to match his prized pool and enlist his daughter's skills to paint a special finishing touch for the home.

episodes.name: Home Dreams Live On
episodes.overview: A mother wants to fulfill her late husband's dream of turning their outdated home into a modern farmhouse. Dave and Jenny bring that dream to life with a basketball court for the kids and some fun personal touches the family can enjoy for years to come.

episodes.name: Storm Chaser Tracks Down Forever Home
episodes.overview: Todd and Trisha Lemery found their future home after Todd was storm chasing in Northwest Arkansas. Now they are ready to start spending more time in their southern home, so they can get away from the brutal northern winters.

episodes.name: Modern Lodge Chalet at Long Last
Midcentury Party House
episodes.overview: A couple who loves the midcentury modern style thought buying a 1970s home made sense, but a pile of renovation projects has them calling for help. Dave and Jenny get to work bringing their groovy pad and party-ready pool house back to its former glory.

episodes.name: City Family Returns to Country Roots
episodes.overview: Now that their kids are older, a family is moving back to their roots in Arkansas. Dave and Jenny step in to help turn their large country home with lots of acreage into a cozy farmhouse where they can focus on "unplugging" with more family time together.

episodes.name: Newlywed Dream Home
episodes.overview: Two newlyweds from Chicago love the house they bought in Arkansas, but they want to put their own personalized stamp on it. Jenny and Dave use the couple's Napa wedding as inspiration to turn the drab brick rancher into a dazzling first home to remember.

episodes.name: Small Rancher Gets the Biggest Addition
Family Home with Aussie Flair
episodes.overview: A couple with Australian roots wants to brighten up their dull '80s rancher and make it better reflect their family's lifestyle; Dave and Jenny give all the kids a special space of their own and update the home with some Aussie inspired touches.

episodes.name: Giving Family Gets Sweet Upgrade
episodes.overview: A couple who has made a positive impact in their community for many years is eager to complete their long-delayed dream house remodel; Dave and Jenny incorporate custom and meaningful touches throughout the family's home, including a sweet surprise.

episodes.name: Dull House to Dazzling Home
episodes.overview: A newly single mum wants to give her early 2000s home a colorful makeover to better reflect her family's vibrant lifestyle; Dave and Jenny transform the home's exterior with smart design choices, along with a beautifully renovated kitchen.

episodes.name: Modern Cabin in the Woods
episodes.overview: A couple purchased a '90s lake house with the hopes of making it their forever home, but it desperately needs an update. Dave and Jenny transform the dated home into a modern cabin-in-the-woods by using the surrounding lush forest as inspiration.

episodes.name: Historic House Revival
episodes.overview: A couple wants to honor the history of their 100-year-old craftsman and make it a functional forever home for their family. Dave and Jenny have a personal connection with the homeowners, so the pressure's on to make this reno perfect for their friends.

episodes.name: Family Farmhouse Restoration
episodes.overview: A couple inherit a home that's been in their family for many years, and they want to turn it into a place for future generations to enjoy; Dave and Jenny transform the home with a renovation that includes meaningful nods to its history.

episodes.name: Rustic Cape Cod Reno
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a dated house with a rustic Cape Cod look.

episodes.name: Log Cabin Turns Forever Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a drab log cabin into a family retreat.

episodes.name: Builder-grade to Craftsman
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny turn a couple's builder-grade house into a custom home.

episodes.name: Cottage Gets a Modern Upgrade
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a historic home with a cottage-inspired look.

episodes.name: Century Old Barn, Family Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a century-old barn into a modern gathering space.

episodes.name: Small House to Cozy Casita
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny help a couple with ties to Peru create their forever home.

episodes.name: California Couple's Dream Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a family's dated rancher into a dream home.

episodes.name: Eccentric House to Modern Home
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny transform a family;'s eccentric interior with a cozy design.

episodes.name: Historic Bank Turned Apartment
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny renovate an apartment for friends and family to stay.

episodes.name: Historic Bank Into Mercantile
episodes.overview: Dave and Jenny construct a mercantile in their historic Centerton building.

episodes.name: Drab Fixer to Charming Cottage
episodes.overview: A first-time homeowner is excited for her English cottage style renovation that she can enjoy with her friends. As demolition gets underway, however, Dave and Jenny uncover an unexpected challenge when they discover her crawl space is filled with water.

episodes.name: A Military Family Gets a Dream Renovation
episodes.overview: The pressure's on for Dave and Jenny as they look to give a military family an unforgettable makeover. With deployment coming soon, however, Dave and Jenny need to work against the clock to finish the renovation in time for this deserving family

episodes.name: Trading Texas Roots for a Horse Ranch Dream
episodes.overview: A family decides to uproot their lives in Texas for their new home in Arkansas. They're looking for the ultimate horse ranch renovation, but as Dave and Jenny dive into the makeover, they encounter issues that could result in major budget adjustments.

episodes.name: Cozy Lake House Reno
episodes.overview: A woman aims to renovate her home on the lake in Rogers, Arkansas. The backyard is treacherous and unusable, so Dave and Jenny look to take advantage of her amazing views to create the ultimate lakeside hangout for her and her family.

episodes.name: Small Historic Home Meets Full Potential
episodes.overview: A young couple purchased a small century old home for their family of three, and the place is in desperate need of a revival. The house is a piece of Bentonville history, and now Dave and Jenny face big challenges as they aim to bring it back to life.

episodes.name: A Grand Makeover Meets the Marrs
episodes.overview: A ballroom dancing California couple is ready for a renovation, and for the Marrs, it's their most grand and unique home yet. Dave and Jenny take on the massive project as they aim to create a bathroom spa-retreat, a chef's kitchen and a formal entryway.

episodes.name: Bland Rancher Gets Global Upgrade
episodes.overview: A couple reconnects after years of dating, and now they're moving in together and want to make major updates to their home. As a nod to their time spent traveling, Dave and Jenny look to add traces of the world to create the couple's unique renovation.

episodes.name: Lakeside House in the Trees
episodes.overview: A couple and their young daughter are ready to update their midcentury three-story house on the lake. There's definite safety concerns within the home, so Dave and Jenny look to navigate the twists and turns of this much needed renovation.

episodes.name: Old Home Brings Big Expectations
episodes.overview: A couple who built their home 20 years ago are ready for an upgrade, and they're looking to modernize the space for family gatherings. Now, Dave and Jenny are challenged to deliver a "Jenny Marrs Kitchen" and the colossal closet they've always dreamt of.

episodes.name: The Ultimate Cabin
episodes.overview: A single mother and her son are ready to update their small cabin, and they're seeking a sense of comfort in the renovation. Dave and Jenny take on the task of transforming their confined space into the ultimate hideaway in the woods.

episodes.name: A Worldwide Home Renovation
episodes.overview: A couple who has lived in the same home for 29 years is ready for a renovation that includes items and memories from their world travels. Dave and Jenny look to incorporate new elements into their updated space while preserving the treasured old.

episodes.name: Rustic Barn to Luxury In-Law Suite
episodes.overview: The Marrs look to convert a barn into an in-law suite and wedding venue for country singer Gabrielle Mooney and her fiance. After surviving a major health crisis, Gabrielle's brother, country singer Shay Mooney, and family help with this special makeover.

episodes.name: Family Home Makeover Helps Tie the Knot
episodes.overview: The renovation continues for a country singer's family home as Dave and Jenny work under a tight deadline to transform her home before her wedding date arrives.

episodes.name: Lakeside Home Reno Brings Family Ties
episodes.overview: Dave's aunt and uncle are moving to Arkansas to be closer to their daughters and family, and they're ready for a lake house renovation. Dave and Jenny feel the pressure as they're tasked to create a relaxing and functional space for the family.

episodes.name: Forever Home on the Lake
episodes.overview: A Texas couple that recently relocated to Arkansas finds help from Dave and Jenny to turn their bland lakeside home into an up-to-date space.

episodes.name: Marrs Family Farmhouse Renovation
episodes.overview: It's a mix of emotions as the Marrs take on a special renovation of their own family farmhouse. Dave and Jenny face the unexpected and embrace some big changes as they prepare to say goodbye to the old home and adjust to their new space.
